    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298184</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>退くぞ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298348</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……よかった……
ふたりとも、無事で……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Phew... I'm so glad to see
you both safe and sound...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298428</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ご、ごめん……
オレ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I...I'm sorry...I shouldn't have—</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298512</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_024&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ううん……
わたしもごめんなさい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No...I should be the one apologizing...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298572</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-What? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>勝手に色々想像してたのは
わたしも同じだもん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I also want everything to go my way.
Sometimes it's unbearable...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298720</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>で、勝手にたくさん
怖がってて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And I constantly drown people
in my own insecurities...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298852</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、そんな不安とかって、
思い過ごしだったのかなって
最近、思うようになったんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But as of late, I realized they
may be groundless fears.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>思い過ごし？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Groundless fears?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>怖いって思ってたことが、
それほど怖くなかったり</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The things that I fear most
maybe aren't all that scary.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>すごいって思ってたことが
それほどすごくなかったり……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The things that I feel are impossible
maybe aren't impossible after all.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>たぶん……この先もたくさん
不安が出てきてそのたびに
逃げたくなるよ、きっと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>For a while back there...I was so scared
of the world, I wanted to just run away
as far as I possibly could.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも……逃げないで、
正面から向き合わなきゃ
何もわかんないままだって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But, if you don't face your
fears head on, then you'll
never understand anything.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299332</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう思った</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've learned that on this journey.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299448</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んなこと言って
向き合ってみて、やっぱ
コワかったらどーすんだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you mean, even if we're really
scared, we should face it with
all we got? Then what?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299588</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね……
そういうこともあるかも。
その時は……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes... That's what I'm talking
about. After that...</EnglishText>
      <Notes>tl check </Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299588</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……どうしよっか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, then what?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>tl check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、なんだよ、それ！
考えてねーのかよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>H-Hey! Don't make fun of me!
I was just thinking out loud!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299808</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その時は、その時かなって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When that time comes, we'll
do what we think it's best!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299808</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_040&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも……なんとかなるよ、
きっと</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm certain we'll be able to face
anything... I'm sure of that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんとかなんて
ならねーよ、ったく……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wow, &lt;Mel&gt; talking about facing
anything. Now this is weird...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>299956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>答え期待したオレが
バカみてーじゃんか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And then you say I'm the idiot?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ゴメンね？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Excuse me?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>べつに。いーけどさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Still...everything's fine, I guess.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300152</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Phew...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、何の音！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wh-What's that noise!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>26</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>300296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_040_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>家の中で聞こえた……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's coming from inside the house...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
